data.description: Welcome to the epitome of country living on this 10-acre property that seamlessly blends functionality with natural beauty. Inside the residence, you'll find warmth and charm at every turn. With 3 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths, this property is designed for comfortable living. The wrap-around porch invites you to unwind and soak in the breathtaking views of your partially wooded property.  A beautiful brick fireplace takes center stage, creating a cozy focal point for gatherings during chilly evenings. The kitchen has been tastefully updated, blending modern convenience with timeless appeal. Hardwood floors throughout the home add a touch of elegance, while the partial wooded property provides a natural backdrop that enhances the overall beauty of the surroundings.    A standout feature of this property is the impressive 46x64 pole barn, offering versatility that caters to both hobbyists and equine enthusiasts alike. The barn is intelligently split, providing a dedicated shop space with a concrete floor for your projects and a horse barn complete with stalls for your four-legged friends.    As you explore the grounds, you'll be captivated by the tranquil creek that meanders through the property and a shared pond, adding a touch of serenity to your everyday life. Whether you're an equestrian or simply appreciate the calming sounds of nature, this feature sets the stage for an idyllic rural lifestyle.    For the handy homeowner or outdoor enthusiast, the deep garage is a treasure trove of possibilities. With ample space for a workshop or boat storage, the potential is limitless. Imagine converting this space into an additional living area or recreational zone to suit your unique needs.  This property isn't just a home; it's a lifestyle. With a perfect balance of practical amenities and natural allure, it invites you to create lasting memories in a setting that feels like a retreat.
